Subject: [PATCH 7/8] ARM: dma-mapping: use alloc, mmap, free from dma_ops
In-reply-to: <1323448798-18184-1-git-send-email-m.szyprowski@samsung.com>
Message-id: <1323448798-18184-8-git-send-email-m.szyprowski@samsung.com>
